question: Show graphic designer positions and web developer positions at 2/7 London Street offices.
sql_query1:
SELECT Position.title 
FROM Position
WHERE (Position.creative_industry_profession = "Graphic Designer" OR Position.creative_industry_profession = "Web Developer") AND Position.office = "2/7 London Street"
sql_query2:
SELECT Position.title 
FROM Position
WHERE Position.creative_industry_profession = "Graphic Designer" OR Position.creative_industry_profession = "Web Developer" AND Position.office = "2/7 London Street"
interpretation1: What graphic designer positions are at 2/7 London Street offices and what web developer positions are at the same location?
interpretation2: List all graphic designer positions and also list web developer positions at 2/7 London Street offices.
